Minecraft 1.21 Tutorial Playlist ► http://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLEB388783144C45A8
Minecraft 1.21 introduced the Crafter! This auto crafting block needed a simple contraption to aid all auto crafting needs. The UCM is my answer, a universal crafter modual you can use over and over again for lots of crafting automation in Minecraft 1.21
